2,"uid":17838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T10:13:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e6f721e351a72edb46524ce88e1e233fed9a9fe1","tid":1593852,"uid":75440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T10:51:14.000Z","msg":"e"},{"pid":"ccbfcf054074d2ba6c9d47ea409fc58f779b1f2e","tid":1593852,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T14:12:52.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Surfshark VPN AC 開心些牙 (已課金)</span></span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wkG4nBJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwkG4nBJ.png&h=15e46738&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請各位自律，<br />\n唔好亂改密碼，<br />\nthx <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>溫馨提示：無論你用緊電腦定電話版APP，<br />\n都一定一定要開 kill switch 至好連 VPN！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\nWindows:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BG4v5Ei.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBG4v5Ei.png&h=9cc93906&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\niOS:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JwgWYkH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJwgWYkH.png&h=102acdf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">極不專業 VPN 速度測試 (WIFI)</span></strong><br />\nSurfshark VPN Server: 日本 M247<br />\nSpeedtest Server: QTS HK<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vc3s7SX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvc3s7SX.png&h=caf32e22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">有關共用 VPN 帳號的安全問題</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/kntgqiX\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/kntgqiX</a><br />\n<br />\nQ: 同鬼share同一個account我唔知會唔會有問題。之前有朋友講過好似佢會拎到你encryption個key同果set encrypted既data，變相佢有心裝你你就會仆街，我朋友做網路保安，佢話如果share同一個account就會share同一條encryption key，share左同一條key就唔存在要破解既問題，因為已經開埋估。<br />\n<br />\nA: 同一個account 最多只係share 同一個credential用黎做 user authentication (by VPN provider)，VPN connection 既 encryption key 應該係create connection個陣既 key exchange 黎 share secret between VPN server and VPN client，而呢個key exchange 唔需要知道 user credential都可以做到，所以理論上只有VPN server 同 VPN client (i.e. your device) 有個encryption key。"},{"pid":"9a8ab6973b0853a0908d89e44f0d5ae72efdfc07","tid":1593852,"uid":75440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T17:00:21.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"5c4aaa6911875ccf4322eb082a00badf893ed54e","tid":1593852,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a8ab6973b0853a0908d89e44f0d5ae72efdfc07","tid":1593852,"uid":75440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T17:00:21.000Z","msg":"1"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T01:29:42.000Z","msg":"2"}]}